      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then she had enough, so she said, what you think that these are agriculture?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How long do you think you will last there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
