      "text": "I always speak some girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I explained to them, we have to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I can't carry for 600 people, so who is volunteering?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if they didn't, so I said, you have to come.",
